		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You can drag either of the effects either off this item or from the Enchantments compendium. This will add the relevant property and adjust the value of the item.</em></p><p><em>Weapon (Any Simple or Martial)</em></p><p>This weapon is &amp;reference[cold iron].</p><p>Cold iron is not a magical material itself, but creating it usually involves the use of magic. Unlike steel or the iron used in most conventional products, cold iron is pure from both chemical and magical impurities through a rigorous process that requires specific equipment and training.</p><ul><li><p>Most fey are resistant or immune to non-cold iron weapons. Cold iron weapons can also be used against incorporeal undead (though magic weapons also work).</p></li></ul>",
